text: Fiona Ma (born March 4, 1966) is an American accountant and politician. She has been the treasurer for the state of California since January 7, 2019. She was a member of the California Board of Equalization (2015–2019), the California State Assembly (2006–2012), and the San Francisco Board of Supervisors (2002–2006), Ma is a member of the Democratic Party. == References == Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from San Francisco Category:Politicians from New York City Category:Accountants Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
